# Agent rule live wire (registry → nerves)

**SSOT:** `data/agent-rule-live-wire-registry-v1.json`  
**Orchestrator:** `python3 scripts/agent_rule_live_wire_v1.py`  
**Law:** `AGENT_DISK_LIVE_WIRE_FIRST_LOCKED_v1.md` · checkcart W12

## Founder plan (non-negotiable)

- **Factories = CLOUD only** (FBE Railway/public · CF workers · product sites)
- **Mac = control panel only** (`:13020` hub) — never plan or gate as a factory
- **Authority:** `data/brain-cloud-practical-300-plan-v1.json` · `CLOUD_ONLY`

## When a new rule ships

1. **R1–R8** — SSOT · script · register row · nerve · surfaces · loops · validator  
2. **R9 / R11** — **One tap after every new `.mdc` or registry row:**

```bash
python3 scripts/agent_rule_live_wire_v1.py --on-new-rule --json
```

Alias: `--upgrade-disk-machines` · lighter: `--wire-sync --skip-heavy --json`

This runs:
- **Cursor rules index** — `~/.sina/cursor-rules-index-v1.json` (all `.mdc` on disk)  
- **Memory mirror** — scans new rules into inject SSOT  
- **Disk** — anti-staleness · live surfaces · factory-now · queue unify · ACTIVE_NOW  
- **Registry pulse** — all live rules → `agent-live-surfaces-v1.json`  
- **Nerves** — better loop + nerve patch  
- **Machines** — H2 `/machines/` `RULE-WIRE-*` rows + `cursor_rules_index` on `h2-pending-registry-v1.json`

## Scaffold

```bash
python3 scripts/agent_rule_live_wire_v1.py --scaffold <rule_id> --json
```

## Every session (automatic)

Registry rules pulse via `disk_live_wire_sync_v1.py` → `rule_live_wire_line` on `agent-live-surfaces-v1.json`.

## Validator

```bash
bash scripts/validate-agent-rule-live-wire-v1.sh
```
